<br>
I have seen copy of 2 SoL mage nukes dropped from Doomshade and Rumblecrush. The thing is that wizards has some disadvantages on mobs who drops EER. Sunstrike for example VP is out of question. Like Luxum said no one... and I mean NO ONE will camp it to get SS, since its such a time sink and requires liek 2 groups completing the key quest. Kunark dragons are now for lower tier guilds which most of the high end guild ignore completely except those who are greedy. Emperor, appart from hierophant cloak I believe not many are looking forward to camp that place anymore ( atleast they are too busy going for better loots elsewhere ). <br>
<br>
EER, well THO is not a very desirable target. Being a pain in the ass of crossing the brindge, the repop is very high and him taking about 30min to kill (average that I heard) and he does not bring much benefit to other classes. Doomshade and Rumblecrush  and also Rhags gives some nice items appart from Spells. So they are more popular in my guild at least. That makes 2 spells out of my way, not to mention GSS which is EMP camp which require its own preparation.<br>
<br>
Availability of the spells has been an issue for us for the last 3 expantions. I know Torpor and Malo for shamans, and Emisary of Thule for necro is also rare ( but i doubt it... Emisary of Thule dropped from emp in crypt ). However, they have other roles that can use while trying to get those spells. For us wizards without nukes there is no way that can improve us significantly except for getting new AAs. ( mind you i bet SS &gt; DoF with SCF3 )<br>
<br>
I don't care if mages get the new nukes. Good better for them and for the group to have a bit more DSP. How ever the way they achieve it makes frustrating for the Designers, not mages but the people who actually put the spell into vendor, makes us very annoying. Many of us are missing SS because its VERY rare and also VERY expensive when u see it on market. EER and GSS are no different in availability. They might not be rare in achieving it, but the mobs that drops em are not very beneficial to the raid force or they are not ready... takes time to get ready etc. (Tho also needs preparation like getting Remove curse to all healers, which they are sold for 4k in TP).<br>
<br>
I am 100% for making SS vendor sold, even tho I got my copy from Gore I really do. EER and GSS or maybe just EER could be quested. My guild nor I think any1 is now interested in confronting THO just for the sake of a wizard spell.<br>
